name: firefox
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "73.0" %}

package:
  name: firefox
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/linux-x86_64/en-US/firefox-{{ version }}.tar.bz2  # [linux64]
  sha256: 96f6a99dc984590acb93814e28e52028f2c764302426bef90c70a7e5a115b037  # [linux64]

  fn: firefox.pkg  # [osx]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/mac/en-US/Firefox%20{{ version }}.pkg  # [osx]
  sha256: 516e8290906fe3a233553ce0d734a6a71586499db0dafc094261643a86818446  # [osx]

  fn: firefox.msi  # [win]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/win64/en-US/Firefox%20Setup%20{{ version }}.msi  # [win]
  sha256: 48b8655d11e143d3ecbf35caf2615a26beb0657f14062275515df187d05d2498  # [win]

build:
  number: 0
  binary_relocation:
    - bin/firefox

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}

test:
  requires:
    - selenium
    - geckodriver

about:
  home: https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/releases
  license: MPL-2.0
  license_family: MOZILLA
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Firefox web browser'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - birdsarah
    - ocefpaf
    - bollwyvl
